cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.DS 

The paper discusses the mapping between Turing Machines and Recurrent Artificial Neural Networks, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the potential for machine learning methods, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the integration of approaches akin to Google DeepMind's Neural Turing Machines, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of Nonlinear Dynamical Automata, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the use of continuous time dynamical systems, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
